*httpclient-2.1.2 (19 Nov 2007)

  19 Nov 2007; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> +metadata.xml,
  +httpclient-2.1.2.ebuild:
  Add httpclient-2.1.2. httpclient replaces http-access2, and is developed by
